        "subject": "LU-18924 tests: Add sanity-hsm.ex to skip test_100/105",
        "message": "LU-18924 tests: Add sanity-hsm.ex to skip test_100/105\n\nAdd sanity-hsm.ex to skip test_100/105(LU-18924) when client version\nis older than mds version.\n\nFixes: 39f1380c20 (\"LU-18924 hsm: fix the crash cause by huge max_requests\")\nTest-Parameters: trivial clientversion=2.16 testlist=sanity-hsm\nChange-Id: I012c2dc9af540e4ff2d627759e11b4e6766f832e\nSigned-off-by: Emoly Liu <emoly@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/61074\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\n"
